Package: pose64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Palm OS Emulator for modern 64-bit Linux
 POSE64 is a native 64-bit Qt6 port of the Palm OS Emulator (POSE) 3.5.
 It emulates Palm OS devices from the Pilot 1000 through the Palm m515,
 including DragonBall 328, EZ, and VZ processor variants.
 .
 Features include cycle-accurate timer emulation, device skins with
 per-pixel transparency, Gremlins automated testing, session save/restore,
 clipboard synchronization, and HiDPI support.
